{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/7a/f7/174191_crt_uqVpZ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7a/f7/174191_crt_uqVpZ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/7a/f7/174191_crt_uqVpZ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/7a/f7/174191_crt_uqVpZ.jpg"},"name":"しろくま","summary":"白熊是一只怕冷又内向的北极熊，虽然是北极熊但却害怕冷，所以从北方逃跑了出来，带着包袱南下。喜欢一切温暖的东西，像热茶、被窝等。白熊跟企鹅？是好朋友，但却常常为了争抢角落而吵架。\r\n特长：画画\r\n性格：怕生怕冷\r\n兴趣：喝茶","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174191},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg"},"name":"ぺんぎん？","summary":"企鹅？拥有睁不大的眼睛、不太像企鹅的黄绿色身体，还有脚上有蹼。因为身体特征都跟一般企鹅相差甚远，所以自己也不太确定自己是不是企鹅，只记得以前头上曾有过碟子，每一天都忙着寻找自我。实际上是一只河童。\r\n爱吃：小黄瓜\r\n兴趣：阅读、音乐\r\n敌人：爪子(常常被抓到)","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174192},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg"},"name":"とんかつ","summary":"炸猪排是来自炸猪排的边边，面上（鼻子）粉红色的部分是1%的瘦肉，其余是99%肥油及酥脆面衣，因为太油所以被常常吃剩下来，想起过去被吃剩的心理创伤，有时候会显得郁郁寡欢，希望有一天会被吃掉，常常发呆，会用干燥剂除湿保持酥脆，但常常会被麻雀啄去头上的面衣。他是食物，但是可以吃东西\r\n炸猪排良伴：酱汁、芥末、袋子","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174193},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/19/e3/174194_crt_4Vh5m.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/19/e3/174194_crt_4Vh5m.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/19/e3/174194_crt_4Vh5m.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/19/e3/174194_crt_4Vh5m.jpg"},"name":"ねこ","summary":"个性害羞、怯懦，常待在角落抓墙壁，只要躲起来就会很安心。虽然害羞，但其实内心很温暖，常常照顾旁人感受。很在意体型，向往纤细身形和长长的尾巴，但因为爱吃所以身体没线条。\r\n性格：心思细腻\r\n爱吃：猫罐头、鱼、猫草\r\n敌人：蜜柑","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174194},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg"},"name":"とかげ","summary":"拥有大嘴巴、背鳍和水蓝色的身躯。其实是幸存的恐龙，因为怕被抓走所以伪装成蜥蜴的样子，以“蜥蜴”的身份生活，对其他角落生物也紧守着秘密，经常想念大海和母亲，和伪蜗牛是好朋友，而且只有伪蜗牛知道他的秘密。\r\n爱吃：鱼\r\n特长：游泳","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174195},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg"},"name":"ふろしき","summary":"白熊由北方南下的行李，经常被用作不同用途上，例如野餐垫、搬行李、被拿去角落占位子、当作靠垫等。是白熊的好朋友，常被怕冷的白熊裹在身上御寒。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174196},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg"},"name":"ざっそう","summary":"杂草是角落生物中难得积极的角色，每天都展现笑脸，爱结交朋友，梦想是成为花店里的花束，拥有永不放弃的积极态度。双脚是根部，可以用来走路和吸水。跟猫咪是好朋友，常被猫咪浇水呵护。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174197},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg"},"name":"えびふらいのしっぽ","summary":"炸虾尾是因为太硬而被吃剩，跟炸猪排为心灵相通的好朋友。留言会想起以前身体好长的时候，会羡慕在便当里最受欢迎的章鱼，总希望自己有一天会被吃掉。\r\n炸虾尾经典系列：外卖袋、配搭小蕃茄、塔塔酱","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174198},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg"},"name":"たぴおか","summary":"粉圆是在珍珠奶茶被喝剩下来的，因为不好吸所以被放弃。粉圆数量很多，个性别扭，通常面无表情，喜欢乱涂鸦、模仿各种物品，摸起来很有弹性。有红色、黄色、蓝色、紫色、绿色、橙色、深蓝色、黑色和彩色粉圆。黑色粉圆是比其他粉圆个性更加别扭的存在。彩色粉圆为粉圆乐园的员工。\r\n粉圆经典口头禅是：“啊～做不下去了啦～”","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174199},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg"},"name":"ほこり","summary":"积极的角色，有一张笑呵呵的脸蛋，懂得飞，身体轻飘飘的，飞尘是无忧无虑的一群。经常聚集在角落，集合在一起就会变大，也可以分裂成小飞尘。怕水，喜欢待在垃圾桶，一出门就会被风吹走。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174200},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg"},"name":"にせつむり","summary":"伪蜗牛是恐龙的好朋友，是一只向往成为蜗牛的蛞蝓，总是背着外壳假装自己是蜗牛，对自己说谎会感到内疚，常常背上不是壳的东西，像包裹布、粉圆、背包等等。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174201},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg"},"name":"おばけ","summary":"居住在小阁楼里的幽灵，心地善良，因为不想吓坏人所以总是躲起来。碰到喜欢或有趣的东西会打开嘴巴，所以就会容易吓到人，又会提醒自己紧闭嘴巴。喜欢打扫，所以阁楼很干净。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174202},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg"},"name":"ふくろう","summary":"麻雀的好朋友，本身是夜行动物，为了可以常常见到麻雀，所以会努力在白天保持清醒，导致睡眠不足。有时候会睁大眼睛，听说可以召来幸福。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174203},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg"},"name":"ぺんぎん（本物）","summary":"从南方来的企鹅，曾经有和白熊见过面(企鹅(真)和白熊都在北极的时候)(那时候企鹅(真)就在旅行了)，旅行到日本的时候，遇到角落伙伴们，被引到角落去，玩了一段时间就继续旅行了，有一段时间企鹅？忌妒他，不过后来企鹅？和他是好朋友，甚至企鹅(真)万卷书窝窝的时候哭的比白熊还伤心呢！","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174204},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg"},"name":"とかげ（本物）","summary":"是真正的蜥蝪，拥有绿色的身体，跟恐龙感情很好，个性不拘小节，所以未有发现恐龙不是蜥蝪，喜欢无忧无虑的生活。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174205},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg"},"name":"まめマスター","summary":"沉默寡言，开了一间咖啡店。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174206},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg"},"name":"きのこ","summary":"住在森林里，因为头上的蕈伞太小，所以戴了另一个大簟伞在头上，和伪蜗牛是好朋友。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174207},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/36/8d/174208_crt_H8w7Z.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/36/8d/174208_crt_H8w7Z.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/36/8d/174208_crt_H8w7Z.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/36/8d/174208_crt_H8w7Z.jpg"},"name":"もぐら","summary":"住在地底，喜欢睡觉，最高纪录是睡一星期，会因为地面太吵所以爬上来看看，对地面上的角落小伙伴充满好奇心，会模仿其他小伙伴的行为。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174208},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg"},"name":"とかげのおかあさん","summary":"幸存的恐龙，恐龙（伪装成蜥蜴）的母亲。生活在大海里，个性十分温柔。曾经跟恐龙一起生活，但现在分隔两地，被人类当成传说中的水怪。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174209},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg"},"name":"ひよこ？","summary":"被画在魔法立体绘本空白页的角落，为了寻找朋友展开冒险。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":174210}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/54/00/174203_crt_dICvD.jpg"},"summary":"麻雀的好朋友，本身是夜行动物，为了可以常常见到麻雀，所以会努力在白天保持清醒，导致睡眠不足。有时候会睁大眼睛，听说可以召来幸福。","name":"ふくろう","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"猫头鹰"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174203,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/0e/82/174200_crt_5Z64u.jpg"},"summary":"积极的角色，有一张笑呵呵的脸蛋，懂得飞，身体轻飘飘的，飞尘是无忧无虑的一群。经常聚集在角落，集合在一起就会变大，也可以分裂成小飞尘。怕水，喜欢待在垃圾桶，一出门就会被风吹走。","name":"ほこり","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"飞尘"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174200,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6d/95/174205_crt_iAbb9.jpg"},"summary":"是真正的蜥蝪，拥有绿色的身体，跟恐龙感情很好，个性不拘小节，所以未有发现恐龙不是蜥蝪，喜欢无忧无虑的生活。","name":"とかげ（本物）","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"蜥蜴（真）"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174205,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/4a/7a/174210_crt_2jG2T.jpg"},"summary":"被画在魔法立体绘本空白页的角落，为了寻找朋友展开冒险。","name":"ひよこ？","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"小灰鸡？"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174210,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/c3/23/174198_crt_F7BfF.jpg"},"summary":"炸虾尾是因为太硬而被吃剩，跟炸猪排为心灵相通的好朋友。留言会想起以前身体好长的时候，会羡慕在便当里最受欢迎的章鱼，总希望自己有一天会被吃掉。\r\n炸虾尾经典系列：外卖袋、配搭小蕃茄、塔塔酱","name":"えびふらいのしっぽ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"炸虾尾"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":2},"id":174198,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/e0/4e/174209_crt_PBNPD.jpg"},"summary":"幸存的恐龙，恐龙（伪装成蜥蜴）的母亲。生活在大海里，个性十分温柔。曾经跟恐龙一起生活，但现在分隔两地，被人类当成传说中的水怪。","name":"とかげのおかあさん","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"蜥蜴的妈妈"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"第二中文名","v":"恐龙妈妈"}]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174209,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a2/b9/174206_crt_1I6ip.jpg"},"summary":"沉默寡言，开了一间咖啡店。","name":"まめマスター","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"咖啡豆老板"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174206,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/26/0b/174197_crt_gzyTF.jpg"},"summary":"杂草是角落生物中难得积极的角色，每天都展现笑脸，爱结交朋友，梦想是成为花店里的花束，拥有永不放弃的积极态度。双脚是根部，可以用来走路和吸水。跟猫咪是好朋友，常被猫咪浇水呵护。","name":"ざっそう","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"杂草"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":1},"id":174197,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9d/b9/174199_crt_QAfGe.jpg"},"summary":"粉圆是在珍珠奶茶被喝剩下来的，因为不好吸所以被放弃。粉圆数量很多，个性别扭，通常面无表情，喜欢乱涂鸦、模仿各种物品，摸起来很有弹性。有红色、黄色、蓝色、紫色、绿色、橙色、深蓝色、黑色和彩色粉圆。黑色粉圆是比其他粉圆个性更加别扭的存在。彩色粉圆为粉圆乐园的员工。\r\n粉圆经典口头禅是：“啊～做不下去了啦～”","name":"たぴおか","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"粉圆"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174199,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/4e/cf/174202_crt_3qNNj.jpg"},"summary":"居住在小阁楼里的幽灵，心地善良，因为不想吓坏人所以总是躲起来。碰到喜欢或有趣的东西会打开嘴巴，所以就会容易吓到人，又会提醒自己紧闭嘴巴。喜欢打扫，所以阁楼很干净。","name":"おばけ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"幽灵"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174202,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6b/d2/174196_crt_xTtlH.jpg"},"summary":"白熊由北方南下的行李，经常被用作不同用途上，例如野餐垫、搬行李、被拿去角落占位子、当作靠垫等。是白熊的好朋友，常被怕冷的白熊裹在身上御寒。","name":"ふろしき","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"包袱巾"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"第二中文名","v":"裹布"}]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":1},"id":174196,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/69/6e/174193_crt_8vmV5.jpg"},"summary":"炸猪排是来自炸猪排的边边，面上（鼻子）粉红色的部分是1%的瘦肉，其余是99%肥油及酥脆面衣，因为太油所以被常常吃剩下来，想起过去被吃剩的心理创伤，有时候会显得郁郁寡欢，希望有一天会被吃掉，常常发呆，会用干燥剂除湿保持酥脆，但常常会被麻雀啄去头上的面衣。他是食物，但是可以吃东西\r\n炸猪排良伴：酱汁、芥末、袋子","name":"とんかつ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"炸猪排"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":1},"id":174193,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b3/f9/174204_crt_m0uDT.jpg"},"summary":"从南方来的企鹅，曾经有和白熊见过面(企鹅(真)和白熊都在北极的时候)(那时候企鹅(真)就在旅行了)，旅行到日本的时候，遇到角落伙伴们，被引到角落去，玩了一段时间就继续旅行了，有一段时间企鹅？忌妒他，不过后来企鹅？和他是好朋友，甚至企鹅(真)万卷书窝窝的时候哭的比白熊还伤心呢！","name":"ぺんぎん（本物）","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"企鹅（真）"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174204,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/bc/cb/174201_crt_CjIOx.jpg"},"summary":"伪蜗牛是恐龙的好朋友，是一只向往成为蜗牛的蛞蝓，总是背着外壳假装自己是蜗牛，对自己说谎会感到内疚，常常背上不是壳的东西，像包裹布、粉圆、背包等等。","name":"にせつむり","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"伪蜗牛（蛞蝓）"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174201,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/30/ae/174192_crt_URuT6.jpg"},"summary":"企鹅？拥有睁不大的眼睛、不太像企鹅的黄绿色身体，还有脚上有蹼。因为身体特征都跟一般企鹅相差甚远，所以自己也不太确定自己是不是企鹅，只记得以前头上曾有过碟子，每一天都忙着寻找自我。实际上是一只河童。\r\n爱吃：小黄瓜\r\n兴趣：阅读、音乐\r\n敌人：爪子(常常被抓到)","name":"ぺんぎん？","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"企鹅？"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":2},"id":174192,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b0/01/174195_crt_tFhA7.jpg"},"summary":"拥有大嘴巴、背鳍和水蓝色的身躯。其实是幸存的恐龙，因为怕被抓走所以伪装成蜥蜴的样子，以“蜥蜴”的身份生活，对其他角落生物也紧守着秘密，经常想念大海和母亲，和伪蜗牛是好朋友，而且只有伪蜗牛知道他的秘密。\r\n爱吃：鱼\r\n特长：游泳","name":"とかげ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"蜥蜴"},{"key":"别名","value":[]}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":174195,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":null,"birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/e4/43/174207_crt_1Ag1E.jpg"},"summary":"住在森林里，因为头上的蕈伞太小，所以戴了另一个大簟伞在头上，和伪蜗牛是好朋友。","name":"きのこ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"蘑菇"},{"key"